children.subject: Woops, by last semester I meant last fall.

I don't know anything about Math 53, but I had Scanlon for Math 135 last semester. He's great, very fair assignments and exams, and good lectures with an appropriate amount of humor and mathematical history/philosophy mixed in. Highly recommended.
